 state, 21.6 %\nare present as cold, diffuse gas, and 53.9 % are found in the state of a\nwarm-hot intergalactic medium.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Aug 2015 20:08:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 26 Feb 2016 21:00:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-01"}
