 investigated as the source of this more rapid intensity\ndecrease of these nuclei.\n  The spectra of H and He are very similar to each other but both contain more\nlow energy particles than would be expected from a correspondence with the\nheavier nuclei spectra. We believe that this may indicate the presence of a\nlocal (heliospheric) component of these nuclei in addition to the galactic\ncomponent.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Aug 2015 21:03:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-10"}
